 Oh, sorry: I'm saying that currently the online check syntax and the
 button are fighting with each other and that sibling rivalry is
 causing bad behavior (probably more than what you report here in this
 bug, but I'm not sure exactly what...), corrupting internal data
 structures somehow. So my proposed fix is to merely make the button
 not do anything (so there are no longer two things to fight with each
 other).
 
 Does that explain better?
 
 Robby
 
 
